abstract: Highlights for the week include a new report on consumer sentiment and earnings reports from Disney and Coca-Cola.
snippet: Highlights for the week include a new report on consumer sentiment and earnings reports from Disney and Coca-Cola.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS Scheduled for this week are consumer credit data for December (Monday); weekly jobless claims and wholesale trade inventories for December (Thursday); trade deficit for December and the Thomson Reuters/University of Michigan consumer sentiment index (Friday).
